    Account profile settings
</p>

<div class="mb-3">
    <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/{{passport.userId}}/{{passport.avatarId}}.png" height="128" width="auto" class="rounded-circle me-2"><br>
</div>
<b>User ID:</b> {{passport.userId}}<br>
<b>Email:</b> {{passport.email}}<br>
